---
title: Thai Pumpkin & Veggie Curry with Roasted Cashews
description: This classic Thai curry is sure to please everyone in your house. By controlling the heat when you add the yellow curry paste, you can set this curry from fragrant to extra hot. It’s up to you!
image: https://img.hellofresh.com/f_auto,fl_lossy,h_640,q_auto,w_1200/hellofresh_s3/image/5b6bad8e30006c32974b2214-e98c56e8.jpg
